In case there is a cleanup of /dev/* names,
I'd like to also point out this (seen on 2.4.*):
/dev/printers/0
but
/dev/cdroms/cdrom0
./discs/disc0
If there are incompatible changes, it might
be good to cleanup all ugly parts, not only some.
